data.title: Diptyque
data.meta_description: Diptyque is a pioneering parfumerie Maison, a precursor of the art of living through the senses, where fragrance and art are integral to everything.
data.text:
The Diptyque Archives have officially returned. We invite you to discover fragrant creations from our previous collections. Warm your home with these treasures from the past. Limited quantities available exclusively online through August 18th.

The essence of summer. A sun-drenched eau de toilette, a scented face and body mist, and a weightless hair mist â€“ in just a few simple steps, one effortless ritual, Ilio marks the season with its floral notes and flashes of fig. The senses come to life under a clear Mediterranean sky.
